    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288080/extras/2d23578478f26b644f33a4beb9f0462f.webp?t=1770343580\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险者猫猫在某处古代遗迹中发现了巨大的宝箱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而却被从宝箱里出现的少女带进了异空间之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了逃出生天，猫猫开始了别开生面的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288080/extras/930eb57c84213306e6d1f045f093d9b7.webp?t=1770343580\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌式战斗：</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指令化战斗模式，玩家可选择各色技能的组合来战斗，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并配有辅助卡牌增加战斗效果与变数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有敌人以及部分NPC会以辅助卡形式辅佐战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >技能强化系统：</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过战斗获得点数，点数可用来选择各系技能并加强技能效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D地下城：</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作为3D地下城RPG，各种宝物沉睡其中，并潜伏有强敌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任务系统：</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内分主线支线任务，玩家可在完成任务的同时，推动故事剧情。</p>",
